snippet.title: Succulent (1 minute teaser / demo, free game)
snippet.description:
Succulent is a a short interactive music video game thing where you watch a hunk suck for a few minutes. It is available RIGHT NOW for Windows / Mac OSX / Linux. For more info and download links: http://radiatoryang.itch.io/succulent

game by Robert Yang (@radiatoryang, http://debacle.us)
music is "Waste" by Alejandro Ghersi (http://arca1000000.com), used with permission
